WEBVTT

1
00:58:42.020 --> 00:58:45.620 
- 喔！你一定很厉害\n- 我还行
-Wow! You must be pretty good.\n-I'm all right.

2
00:58:46.660 --> 00:58:50.390 
有时候我觉得，我该给他们钱来签我的名
Sometimes I feel I should be paying them\nto take my autograph.

3
00:58:50.600 --> 00:58:53.290 
对不起，我没注意你叫什么
I'm sorry, I didn't even get your name.

4
00:58:53.600 --> 00:58:57.590 
赖丘，赖丘·斯本森，你是？
Latrell. Latrell Spencer. And you are?

5
00:58:57.670 --> 00:59:01.200 
- 丹尼斯·波特\n- 丹尼斯，丹尼斯·波特
-Denise Porter.\n-Denise. Denise Porter.

6
00:59:01.710 --> 00:59:05.270 
你知道，你看起来很眼熟\n我好象在哪里见过你
You know, you look so familiar.\nI feel like I've seen you somewhere.

7
00:59:05.350 --> 00:59:09.910 
没有，我打球，也许你看过我的比赛
No. I play pro ball.\nMaybe you've seen one of my games.

8
00:59:09.980 --> 00:59:14.650 
没有，但是我想我要是看过的话\n我一定会记得你
No. But I mean if I did, I'm sure\nI would've definitely remembered you.

